text: Yo @AppleSupport and @UPSHelp - this preordered #iphone was due in Philly PA 9/21, apple staff insisted via phone last night it would come today and guess what? ANOTHER #delivery exception! I'm not impressed at all. https://t.co/rUKPThBWIq

@webhill I know how frustrating it can be to not get a phone when you have been waiting on it. If you would like us to take a deeper look into this please DM us your tracking number, complete address, phone number, and the name on this package. ^AC
